Package org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver

Class TestSeekOptimizations

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.TestSeekOptimizations
public class TestSeekOptimizations extends Object
Test various seek optimizations for correctness and check if they are actually saving I/O operations.
